description: Buckets of related memes; may have parents/children.
parents: []     # 0..n parent slugs
aliases: []    # optional
---

An adjective rather than a noun, this concept presents in many memes. In the most general sense it represents monotonically iterative structures, or progressive abstractions, or example, subsampling an image or smoothing an image in progressive degrees to represent varying shades of abstraction or specificity would constitute a hierarchical abstraction (a [[multiscale]] representation). 

